title: The Power of Oneness - Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: The Power of Oneness - Victoria Osteen
description:
The Bible says when believers dwell together in unity, “there the LORD commanded the blessing—life forevermore” (Psalm 133:3). It is only the love of God that brings people to the arms and saving power of Jesus Christ. God is saying it’s up to us to keep in unity and the bond of peace.
